            "url": "https://lib0gus.github.io/2026/05/19/Java%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%AE%A1%E8%AE%A1/Day1%20%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/",
            "title": "Day1 环境搭建",
            "date_published": "2026-05-19T07:21:19.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"1-安装-jdk\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1-安装-jdk\">#</a> 1. 安装 JDK</h2>\n<p>Java 安全研究通常需要多个 JDK 版本，因为不同版本的安全限制差异很大。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>JDK 8</strong> — 最重要的版本，大量反序列化漏洞利用链基于它</li>\n<li><strong>JDK 11</strong> — LTS，很多企业生产环境在用</li>\n<li><strong>JDK 17</strong> — 新 LTS，高版本安全特性</li>\n</ul>\n<p>配置系统环境变量 <code>JAVA_HOME</code>，指向 JDK 安装目录。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>为什么需要多个版本？</strong></p>\n<p>很多反序列化漏洞在 JDK 8 上可以直接利用，但高版本 JDK 因为模块化、反射限制等安全增强，需要额外的绕过技巧。审计时也需要判断目标应用用的是哪个版本。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"2-安装-idea\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2-安装-idea\">#</a> 2. 安装 IDEA</h2>\n<p>下载安装 IntelliJ IDEA（社区版免费，旗舰版功能更多，对于代码审计来说社区版足够）。</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-安装和配置-maven\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#3-安装和配置-maven\">#</a> 3. 安装和配置 Maven</h2>\n<p>Maven 是 Java 项目的构建和依赖管理工具，核心功能：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>项目构建</strong> — 编译、测试、打包、部署一条命令搞定</li>\n<li><strong>依赖管理</strong> — 自动下载和管理第三方库，不用手动拷贝 jar 包</li>\n<li><strong>标准化项目结构</strong> — 约定优于配置，所有 Maven 项目结构一致</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"31-下载\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#31-下载\">#</a> 3.1 下载</h3>\n<p>前往 <a href=\"https://maven.apache.org/download.cgi\">Maven 官网</a> 下载最新版本，解压到本地目录。</p>\n<h3 id=\"32-配置环境变量\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#32-配置环境变量\">#</a> 3.2 配置环境变量</h3>\n<p>将 Maven 的安装目录加入系统环境变量 <code>MAVEN_HOME</code>，再将 <code>bin</code> 目录加入 <code>Path</code>：</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"1779186206531.png\" alt=\"1779186206531\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"1779186248203.png\" alt=\"1779186248203\" /></p>\n<p>打开命令行，输入 <code>mvn -version</code> 验证是否配置成功：</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"1779186308578.png\" alt=\"1779186308578\" /></p>\n<h3 id=\"33-修改配置文件\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#33-修改配置文件\">#</a> 3.3 修改配置文件</h3>\n<p>在 Maven 根目录下创建 <code>repository</code> 文件夹作为本地仓库：</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"1779186416947.png\" alt=\"1779186416947\" /></p>\n<p>进入 <code>conf</code> 目录，编辑 <code>settings.xml</code>，配置本地仓库路径和阿里云镜像：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">localRepository</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">F:\\maven\\maven_repository</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">/</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">localRepository</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span></code></pre>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"1779186481169.png\" alt=\"1779186481169\" /></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>建议同时配置阿里云镜像，加快依赖下载速度。在 <code>&lt;mirrors&gt;</code> 节点中添加：</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">mirror</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    </span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">id</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">aliyun</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">/</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">id</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    </span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">mirrorOf</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">central</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">/</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">mirrorOf</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    </span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">name</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">aliyun maven</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">/</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">name</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    </span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">url</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">https://maven.aliyun.com/repository/public</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">/</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">url</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">&#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">/</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">mirror</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">></span></span></code></pre>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"34-配置-idea-中的-maven\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#34-配置-idea-中的-maven\">#</a> 3.4 配置 IDEA 中的 Maven</h3>\n<p>打开 IDEA，进入 <strong>文件 → 设置 → 构建、执行、部署 → 构建工具 → Maven</strong>：</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"1779186558233.png\" alt=\"1779186558233\" /></p>\n<p>修改 <strong>Maven 主路径</strong> 和 <strong>用户设置文件</strong> 为自己安装的 Maven 路径：</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"1779186593381.png\" alt=\"1779186593381\" /></p>\n<p>本地仓库路径会自动同步，点击应用即可。</p>\n<h2 id=\"4-创建第一个项目\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#4-创建第一个项目\">#</a> 4. 创建第一个项目</h2>\n<p>用 IDEA 创建一个 Maven 项目，写一个 HelloWorld 确认环境能跑通。</p>\n<h2 id=\"5-一键切换-jdk-版本脚本\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#5-一键切换-jdk-版本脚本\">#</a> 5. 一键切换 JDK 版本脚本</h2>\n<p>日常需要频繁切换 JDK 版本，每次手动改环境变量很麻烦，这里写了一个 bat 脚本，以管理员身份运行即可一键切换。</p>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-bat\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">@</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> off</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">chcp</span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\"> 65001</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> </span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">></span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">nul</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">title</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> Java 永久切换工具 </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">需要管理员权限</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> ==========================================</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">   警告：此操作将永久修改系统环境变量</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> ==========================================</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> 请选择要设置为默认的 Java 版本：</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> 1. JDK 1.8</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> 2. JDK </span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">11</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> 3. JDK </span><span style=\"color:#2F798A;--shiki-dark:#4C9A91\">17</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> 4. JDK 1.8.0_102</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">echo</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">.</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">set</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> /p </span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">choice</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">请输入选项（1/2/3/4）：</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">REM</span><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\"> 定义路径</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">if</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> \"</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">%</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">choice</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">%</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">==</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">1</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\"> set</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> TARGET_PATH</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">=</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">C:\\Program Files </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">(</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">x86</span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">)</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">\\Java\\jdk-1.8</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">if</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> \"</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">%</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">choice</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">%</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">==</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C